    <div class="content"><p>"For some reason the Colony which is a movable ship, is on a frozen sea under a purple sky on some planet. Not sure why. There are two other Cylon base ship type structures behind the mountains too. This may be the Cylon homeworld."</p>
<p>There is a also a clearly visible small Cylon basestar on the right, above the SciFi HD logo, which makes the Colony a humongous structure.<br />
But the "mountain range in the distance" doesn't really look like mountains to me - more like parts of a huge ship. I am not convinced the Colony is on a planet, although it may be. It is hard to tell from all that purple haze.</p>
