<p>* I last saw someone make this sort of effort years ago when discussing games and keyboard mappings. Someone came up with a colour coded keymap and matching explanation. I was really impressed with that. It condensed a very tricky discussion into something instantly understandable. I haven't seen anyone British spring to something like this.</p>
